            <p>The Covid-19 Advisory Portal is a one-stop platform for authenticated data and news regarding the novel
                coronavirus situation in INDIA. The portal acts as a reliable repository of advisories and information
                regarding Covid-19 along with information on various initiatives taken by the District Administrations
                in this time of crisis.

                The portal has a real-time dashboard which shows the number of confirmed, active, recovered and dead
                cases along with a State-wise break-up of data. The State Dashboards which shows the state wise
                figures, the initiatives taken by the State Administration and any State specific orders available
                for citizens.

                Citizens can directly access important links such as ePass for essential services, Dhanwantari scheme
